            <p><q class="fancy-quotes">The druid is a formidable class with good healing ability, potent offensive spells, excellent buffs, and the unique ability to shapeshift into different animal types. In its animal forms, the druid can adopt new roles, such as that of a warrior or rogue, giving it great versatility.</q>--World
