            <section>
                <h3>Viability of Restoration Druid Healers in WoW Classic PvE content</h3>
                <p>Healing Druids are extremely viable in Classic WoW and can fill both "Raid Healing" roles, as well as "Tank Healing" roles. Most raids will usually bring 1-3, as what they lack in their ability to do healing/damage they compensate by having
                    lots of utility.
                </p>
                <p>Even though they are strong, their place in a 40 man raid is usually restricted, as the HoTs effects of healing abillities are unique to a target, meaning that other druids cant stack <a href="https://classic.wowhead.com/spell=774/rejuvenation"
                        class="yellow-text">Rejuvenation</a> on the same target for example.</p>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h3>Strenghts and Weaknesses</h3>
                <section>
                    <h4>Strenghts</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Tons of utility with abillities like : <a href="https://classic.wowhead.com/spell=24752/mark-of-the-wild" class="yellow-text">Mark of the Wild</a>,<a href="https://classic.wowhead.com/spell=29166/innervate" class="yellow-text">Innevrate</a>,
                            <a href="https://www.wowhead.com/spell=65863/faerie-fire" class="yellow-text">Faerie Fire</a>, <a href="https://classic.wowhead.com/spell=20484/rebirth" class="yellow-text">Rebirth</a>.</li>
                        <li>Hybrid talent choice, meaing that u can do almost everything in the game with little effort, like tanking, meele DPS, range DPS.</li>
                        <li>Combat Ress.Druids are the only class that can combat ress in WoW classic which is sometimes the difference of wiping in a raid, and managing to kill the boss.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h4>Weaknesses</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>No normal ress ability.When you wipe in WoW, healers have to ress the entire 40-man raid which can take a while, so every healer has to ress but as druids you just sit and watch.</li>
                        <li>Don't expect to be the top of the charts. In a optimal scenario, other healers such as priests should be able to out-heal you most of the time.</li>
                    </ul>
